<h2>Compatibility</h2>

<p>This namespace includes libraries which improve cross-browser compatibility.</p>

<h3>IE7 Compatibility</h3>

<p>These modules are loaded into the <code>blocks-ie.css</code> build file and targeted at IE7 specifically:</p>

<ul class="modules">
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render('Compatibility/IE/Image/Scaling') %></li>
</ul>

<p><em>NOTE: The <code>Compatibility/IE/Image/Scaling</code> only supports JPEG images. The package <a href="#API/Package/ie7imagescaling">alphaimagescaling</a> may be enabled to provide image scaling support for additional image types such as PNG and GIF.</em></p>

<h3>IE8 and Below Compatibility</h3>

<p>These modules are loaded into the <code>blocks-ie.css</code> build file and thus target IE8 and below:</p>

<ul class="modules">
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render('Compatibility/IE/CSS/Filter/Border_Radius') %></li>
</ul>

<h3>Capability Testing</h3>

<p>These modules provide Javascript functions and properties that allow one to test whether or not a browser supports all WebBlocks required or recommended features:</p>

<ul class="modules">
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render_details('Compatibility/Support') %></li>
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render_details('Compatibility/Support/CSS') %></li>
    <li><%= DOC.modules.render_details('Compatibility/Support/HTML') %></li>
</ul>
